    "post-quiz-closer": {
      "type": "post-quiz-closer",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Your smile is next.",
        "content": "<p>I have had patients tell me they have not smiled in a photo in five years. The smile is the point, and everything else is just how we get you there.</p><p>The smile is ready. The only thing left is the decision.</p>",
